      "sha256": "d32886ab56bcb4ca3658e8832e9f41187467337fce0ee9992db8d6ea2b65e0b1",
      "request": {
        "text": "Karl CCLV, lyssna noga. Flottan håller kursen genom mörkret och ingen lämnas bakom oss. Instrumenten visar främmande signaler mellan gruvmånarna. Jag vill ha lugn eld, öppna ögon och full kontroll över skeppet tills vi vet vem som följer oss.",
        "language": "sv",
        "voice_instruction": "An adult Swedish female general-admiral, composed and authoritative, low warm register, crisp military diction, restrained urgency, natural Swedish pronunciation, never theatrical or breathy.",
        "model_backend": "voxcpm2",
        "output_format": "wav",
        "normalize": false,
        "seed": 302021
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "reference",
      "role": "soren-svartkrut",
      "job_id": "a572686db571433aa8d8513e32011d55",
      "file": "assets/stormakt3020/radio/references/soren-svartkrut-reference.wav",
      "sha256": "e19709a51ae6c6812929fd449432e783b80c766992bb3aefca1a3a3be5f88b0b",
      "request": {
        "text": "Ni blårockar färdas långt från era kartor. Här bär varje sten ett namn och varje mörk signal har ett minne. Jag heter Sören Svartkrut. Håll fingret från avtryckaren, så kanske skogen låter er passera med både skepp och stolthet i behåll.",
        "language": "sv",
        "voice_instruction": "An adult Scanian male outlaw captain, rugged baritone, dry wit and controlled menace, clear Swedish with a subtle southern Scanian color, intelligent and charismatic, never comic or exaggerated.",
        "model_backend": "voxcpm2",
        "output_format": "wav",
        "normalize": false,
        "seed": 302022
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "reference",
      "role": "rasmus-gyldentold",
      "job_id": "f76d72949e1741d18eb9c894f16f1348",
      "file": "assets/stormakt3020/radio/references/rasmus-gyldentold-reference.wav",
      "sha256": "1999863cbe5cc3a961d56d83786fd55b9b606fad8508eceb615ec189b22eae51",
      "request": {
        "text": "Svenske fartøj, lyt nøje. Jeg er foged Rasmus Gyldentold, og Kronens tiende forfalder i dag. Mine kanoner vogter broerne, mine segl lukker farvandet, og intet skib passerer uden at betale. Læg bi med værdighed, før regnskabet bliver skrevet med jern og ild.",
        "language": "da",
        "voice_instruction": "An adult Danish royal bailiff and warship commander, broad resonant baritone, immaculate formal diction, proud controlled menace, theatrical authority without comedy, natural Danish pronunciation.",
        "model_backend": "voxcpm2",
        "output_format": "wav",
        "normalize": false,
        "seed": 302023
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "reference",
      "role": "kung-christian",
      "job_id": "5f986fda55a449ec91f886e4daaab3a0",
      "file": "assets/stormakt3020/radio/references/kung-christian-reference.wav",
      "sha256": "391fd7d3d32e09408e2fa6cb3e1fc64b8d57600861322173df6e27cffcd70bf9",
      "request": {
        "text": "Alle fregatter frem! Hold Dannebrog højt og luk deres flugtvej! Jeg vil høre kanonerne svare fra hver eneste bro. De svenske blåfrakker har hånet min krone for sidste gang. Bryd deres linje, knus deres skjolde, og driv Karl tohundrede femoghalvtreds levende frem for mig!",
        "language": "da",
        "voice_instruction": "A powerful barrel-chested adult Danish male war king, huge booming rough bass-baritone, loud military projection, gravel and iron in the chest, barking furious orders across cannon fire. Angry Danish naval commander who dominates a battlefield without sounding old, weak, refined, feminine, soft, breathy or comedic. Strong consonants, broad resonance, controlled rage, unmistakably masculine physical power.",
        "model_backend": "voxcpm2",
        "output_format": "wav",
        "normalize": false,
        "seed": 873021
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "reference",
      "role": "birgitte-bille",
      "job_id": "957d2d5cd530476bb9be256f8d3ccab6",
      "file": "assets/stormakt3020/radio/references/birgitte-bille-reference.wav",
      "sha256": "a3c0408d6c2ff93f63413b00db272cff028a5ec10127599c0b02acb7dd16053f",
      "request": {
        "text": "Hør mig, danske søfolk. Jeg er Kommandør Birgitte Bille, og Glimminge Jern bøjer sig hverken for storm, ild eller svenske kroner. Hold skjoldmuren samlet, spænd boret fast og lad hver kanon tale med én stemme. Den, der forlader sin post, skal svare til mig personligt.",
        "language": "da",
        "voice_instruction": "An imposing older Danish female fleet commander, broad powerful contralto, stern matronly authority, huge chest resonance, crisp natural Danish military diction, controlled anger that rises into a formidable battlefield roar, never young, soft, breathy, seductive, shrill, weak or comedic.",
        "model_backend": "voxcpm2",
        "output_format": "wav",
        "normalize": false,
        "seed": 302024
      }
